{
  "stem": "14060.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember I was told when he did his matric in mathematics, he came out as the first and he got top marks in everything.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, that goes within a limited time, but if you finished, you leave the room.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there is, for instance, an interesting anecdote.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We-- we went to the Szechenyi Istvan gymnasium, which was a very highly held grammar school-- gymnasium they called it, a state gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I remember the story being told by my father that it was customary that when child goes to school, you go and inquire from the particular teachers in the grammar school how he is proceeding-- progressing.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the open days, as it's known in English schools, didn't exist, so the parent had to show interest and make visits there, time to time, by appointment and make inquiries.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was a-- a very, very capable mathematics teacher in the Szechenyi Istvan gymnasium, who in fact taught me also.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father, he was born in 1924, so he would have started in 1934 school there, so it was in the period between 1934 and '38 that this happened, because afterwards he went to a specialized academy where he did his matric.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That my father one day went in to inquire, how is my son Erwin Weiler doing?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the teacher, who was quite a nice person, there was nothing wrong with him, answered him, Mr.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Weiler, I only know two sorts of Jews, either very clever or very stupid.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You've got nothing to worry about.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What I am trying to tell a little anecdote, that how open and unashamed the anti-Semitism was.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, this was a sort of a friendly gesture.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was nothing bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was nothing insulting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was the method which was used.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
